reviewText: DVD was great had hapkido, kajukenbo, Krav Maga, also had Brazilian jiu jitsu . All styles where very informative and unique in its own way.

I really enjoyed the segment filmed in Israel and had been looking for a copy of this episode to own, so I was happy to find this DVD. The rest of the DVD was of less interest to me personally, but some other folks may find it interesting.
